  m_text: "You are trapped in a haunted art gallery. On the outside, the gallery
    appears fine- but the closer you look, the weirder things get. \n\nNavigate the
    gallery with W,A,S,D keys. \nPress Shift to walk faster. \nIf you see nothing
    unusual, keep moving forward.\nThe moment something feels off, turn back and
    walk in the opposite direction. \nRepeat these steps till you find your way out
    of the gallery. \n\nWelcome and Best of Luck, dear art connoisseur! "
